```plantuml
@startuml EOS-Nation_dfuse-docs

package "dfuse System" {
    [dfuseeos CLI] as dfuseeos
    [GraphQL API] as graphql
    [gRPC Layer] as grpc
    [Authentication Service] as auth
    [Data Indexing Service] as indexing
    [Streaming Service] as streaming
    [Search Service] as search
    [Storage Abstraction] as storage
    [nodeos Integration] as nodeos
}

package "External Systems" {
    [EOSIO Blockchains] as eosio
    [BigTable/TiKV/Badger] as db
    [Netlify] as netlify
}

dfuseeos --> graphql : manages
dfuseeos --> nodeos : interacts with

graphql --> grpc : uses
graphql --> auth : authenticates via
graphql --> indexing : queries
graphql --> streaming : subscribes to

grpc --> indexing : communicates with
grpc --> streaming : communicates with
grpc --> search : communicates with

indexing --> storage : persists data
streaming --> storage : reads/writes
search --> storage : queries

storage --> db : uses

nodeos --> eosio : connects to

netlify --> graphql : hosts docs for

@enduml
```